message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing techniques for evaluating English essays. Other likely sub-categories could be "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) as machine learning techniques are used, "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) as the paper discusses the use of Latent Semantic Analysis and Maximum Entropy, "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) as the techniques are used for evaluating text, and "cs.DL" (Digital Libraries) as the paper discusses the use of ontology for enhancing the evaluation process.
